<p>Aside from that, I found numerous mentions to &quot;decaying&quot; ghost ships, but none to that level of specificity. However, since that article specifically mentioned Captain Faulkner, I decided to run an additional search through the CoUC archive for the Captain, and I came across this entry from 1821.</p>
