<span style="font-size:180%;"><strong>The R. H. Commission on Unusual Cargo</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:140%;">Authorised by the Board of Regents of said Commission</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="font-family: 'Nothing You Could Do', cursive; font-size: 0.8em;"><span style="font-size:120%;">From The Honorable Reginald Fieldstone, Steward</span><br />
<span style="font-size:120%;">To The Right Honourable Comissioner Othaniel Trower</span><br />
<span style="font-size:120%;">October 14, 1821</span></span></p>
